---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Paul Diaz Ashot — CV">
	<main class="cv-content">
		<header class="cv-header">
			<h1>Paul Diaz Ashot</h1>
			<div class="locations">London, Barcelona, New York</div>
			<div class="contact">
				<a href="mailto:paul.ashot@icloud.com">paul.ashot@icloud.com</a> ·
				(646) 996 5037 ·
				<a href="https://pauldiazashot.com">pauldiazashot.com</a> ·
				@supersonicsines
			</div>
		</header>

		<section>
			<h2>Summary</h2>
			<p>Founder-operator and technical GTM lead with deep experience selling technical products to sophisticated buyers. Founding team at <b>GMX</b>, a decentralised derivatives exchange that scaled to $450M+ TVL and $40M+ annualised revenue with a team of three. Active AI developer since 2023; currently pairs OpenAI GPT-5.5 and Codex CLI with Anthropic Claude to ship production AI deployments including a live, revenue-generating prediction-market analytics platform and a public job-search engine. Native English, fluent Russian, fluent Spanish.</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Experience</h2>

			<div class="role">
				<div class="title"><b>Portico Ventures</b> — <em>Managing Partner</em></div>
				<div class="dates">2021 – 2026</div>
			</div>
			<ul>
				<li>Venture capital fund specialising in advising and investing in early stage DeFi/Fintech. Worked closely on GTM with several portfolio companies including <b>Gammaswap</b> and <b>Codex.io</b>. Influenced <b>$4M+ in aggregate fundraising</b> through advisory work and warm introductions.</li>
			</ul>

			<div class="role">
				<div class="title"><b>GMX</b> — <em>Founding Team · Growth & Partnerships</em></div>
				<div class="dates">2020 – 2023</div>
			</div>
			<ul>
				<li>Three-person founding team. Top DeFi revenue generator during my tenure. Co-led institutional partnerships and capital formation; personally sourced <b>$20M+ in cumulative capital deployments</b>.</li>
				<li>Closed and co-closed strategic partnerships with <em>Arbitrum</em>, <em>Avalanche</em>, <em>Chainlink</em>, and <em>Frax</em>, plus two other protocol integrations. Coordinated the Gambit → GMX rebrand and organised outreach to future partners.</li>
				<li>Built and led the institutional and community channels: 5,000+ Telegram members and direct relationships with eight-figure liquidity providers.</li>
			</ul>

			<div class="role">
				<div class="title"><b>Effie Perine LTD.</b> — <em>Operations & Client Relations</em></div>
				<div class="dates">2019 – 2020</div>
			</div>
			<ul>
				<li>Managed financial accounts and operational administration for a private art dealership specialising in Old Master Pictures; annual transaction volumes in the £500K–£2.5M+ range.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Independent AI Deployments</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><b>Slashwork.xyz</b> — fully live, free AI-deployed job-search engine for the startup and technical community, focused on fresh roles at tracked public-market companies. Built end-to-end with Claude Opus. <a href="https://slashwork.xyz">slashwork.xyz</a>.</li>
				<li><b>Pawlymarket</b> — live scraper and data aggregator using statistical models to identify market inefficiencies. $50K ARR within two months of launch. <a href="https://pawlymarket.com">pawlymarket.com</a>.</li>
				<li><b>Vinted-to-Depop reselling agent</b> — end-to-end autonomous fashion-arbitrage agent operated via Telegram.</li>
				<li><b>Intelligent booking system</b> — Codex CLI-assisted agentic scheduler for a small local business; takes class bookings and organises future classes based on predicted demand.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Education</h2>
			<p><b>BSc Chemistry</b>, <em>University of Manchester</em>, 2018.</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Skills</h2>
			<p class="skills">Technical GTM & account strategy · consultative selling to technical buyers · founder/C-level relationships · platform/API product evangelism · enterprise negotiation · founder-network leverage · community-led growth · venture capital · startup operations · risk management · market intelligence · financial modelling · ATS scraping · SQLite/FTS · OpenAI GPT-5.5 · Codex CLI · Claude API · prompt engineering · agentic workflows · MCP · Python · JavaScript</p>
		</section>

		<footer class="cv-footer">
			<a href="mailto:paul.ashot@icloud.com">paul.ashot@icloud.com</a> ·
			<a href="https://t.me/supersonicsines">Telegram</a> ·
			<a href="/Paul_Diaz_Ashot_CV.pdf" download>Download CV (PDF)</a>
		</footer>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.cv-content {
		max-width: 680px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 48px 24px;
		opacity: 1;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.cv-header {
		text-align: center;
		padding-bottom: 16px;
		border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-rule);
		margin-bottom: 24px;
	}

	.cv-header h1 {
		margin: 0 0 8px 0;
	}

	.locations {
		font-size: 16px;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin-bottom: 6px;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.contact {
		font-family: var(--font-sans);
		font-size: 13px;
		color: var(--color-muted);
		margin-bottom: 4px;
	}

	section {
		margin-bottom: 24px;
	}

	h2 {
		margin: 0 0 12px 0;
		padding-bottom: 6px;
		border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-rule);
	}

	.role {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: baseline;
		margin: 12px 0 4px 0;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 4px;
	}

	.role .title {
		font-size: 16px;
	}

	.role .dates {
		font-family: var(--font-sans);
		font-size: 13px;
		color: var(--color-muted);
		font-style: italic;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	p {
		margin: 0 0 8px 0;
	}

	ul {
		margin: 4px 0 12px 0;
		padding-left: 20px;
		list-style: none;
	}

	li {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 16px;
		margin-bottom: 6px;
	}

	li::before {
		content: "–";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--color-ink);
	}

	.skills {
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.cv-footer {
		margin-top: 48px;
		padding-top: 16px;
		border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-rule);
		text-align: center;
		font-family: var(--font-sans);
		font-size: 13px;
		color: var(--color-muted);
	}

	.cv-footer a {
		color: var(--color-ink);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.cv-content {
			padding: 32px 20px;
		}

		.role {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 2px;
		}

		.role .dates {
			font-size: 12px;
		}
	}

	@media print {
		@page {
			size: A4;
			margin: 10mm 11mm;
		}

		:global(html) {
			font-size: 11px;
			line-height: 1.26;
			background: #fff;
		}

		:global(body) {
			background: #fff;
		}

		:global(.overlay) {
			display: none !important;
		}

		.cv-content {
			max-width: none;
			padding: 0;
		}

		.cv-header {
			padding-bottom: 7px;
			margin-bottom: 9px;
		}

		.cv-header h1 {
			font-size: 24px;
			margin-bottom: 3px;
		}

		.locations {
			font-size: 11px;
			margin-bottom: 2px;
		}

		.contact {
			font-size: 9.5px;
			margin-bottom: 0;
		}

		section {
			margin-bottom: 9px;
			break-inside: avoid;
		}

		h2 {
			font-size: 13px;
			margin-bottom: 5px;
			padding-bottom: 2px;
			letter-spacing: 1.8px;
		}

		.role {
			margin: 6px 0 2px 0;
		}

		.role .title {
			font-size: 11px;
		}

		.role .dates {
			font-size: 9.5px;
		}

		p {
			margin-bottom: 4px;
		}

		ul {
			margin: 2px 0 6px 0;
			padding-left: 12px;
		}

		li {
			padding-left: 10px;
			margin-bottom: 3px;
		}

		.skills {
			line-height: 1.35;
		}

		.cv-footer {
			display: none;
		}
	}
</style>
